{"tid":102153,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日食飯比親戚個讀polyu既女串","createTime":"2017-01-31T12:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T18:04:07.000Z","uid":75893,"like":19,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0eb26825652ad604be0d76936d152dcac1741ea","tid":102153,"uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"琴日同成班親戚食飯<br />\n班親戚當然例牌問我讀緊乜<br />\n我就答佢:「讀緊HKU n展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n點知親戚個女(佢讀polyu bba)就插嘴話:「下, but我見你Facebook一張hku既photo都冇wo, well, you know, normally 港大仔去starbucks study都會take a selfie啦, 但你...no offense, in fact你係唔係讀hku SPACE炸?」<br />\n我梗係即刻話唔係, 係銀包拎張學生證黎證明自己讀緊HKU<br />\n點知佢望到我張學生證之後走去google search &quot;hku student card&quot;<br />\n佢見我個張唔match第一張圖, 就開始笑我space扮hku<br />\n但係人都知今年新生換左新卡(<a href=\"http://www.its.hku.hk/news/news181/smart-card-upgrade\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.its.hku.hk%2Fnews%2Fnews181%2Fsmart-card-upgrade&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=bb13c445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.its.hku.hk/news/news181/smart-card-upgrade</a>)<br />\n我嘗試反駁「唔..唔係呀....今..今年..轉..轉左」, 但條港女又聽唔到, 成班親戚已經開始信哂我係讀HKU space, 老豆成程飯都黑面冇講野, 點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4945a5f729ae5eb647e8861ee5700155affa85ae","tid":102153,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"f4e8be4b1abee261e33421cc31b28eb2c517e0f4","tid":102153,"uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點知佢望到我張學生證之後走去google search &quot;hku student<span style=\"color: red;\"> id </span>card&quot;</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5b9e04c2fb34e1e740dd3b2fb56827ca1e139ce2","tid":102153,"uid":53800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>渣ga</blockquote><br />\n渣ga"},{"pid":"a5e5284e85e149fc347c3510c3b396cc